position":{"start":{"line":117,"column":1},"end":{"line":120,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"· 起点：为自己和公司喂养“赛博果苗”（第二大脑），尝试让知识库、AI、自己组成新系统。\n· 挫折：过程痛苦，“教一个婴儿学步”，“他是个转头就忘的笨蛋”。\n· 突破：找到精巧结构，系统开始自我产出内容并外溢智慧（如项目经理的反馈、秘书的感动）。\n· 终点：“活的系统会滋养每个身在系统中的人”，他把自己对“活”的期待，物化成了真正的生态。","position":{"start":{"line":117,"column":1},"end":{"line":117,"column":1}},"key":"wjITN0dfjU"}],"key":"FrIpaO79VS"},{"type":"list","ordered":true,"start":4,"spread":false,"position":{"start":{"line":122,"column":1},"end":{"line":123,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":122,"column":1},"end":{"line":123,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"哲学线索：从“偏见”到“共识”的认知跃迁","position":{"start":{"line":122,"column":1},"end":{"line":122,"column":1}},"key":"AFQWTAXhrd"}],"key":"fgqPyNAKYJ"}],"key":"zk7odaEbA3"}],"key":"KLwulPISd0"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":124,"column":1},"end":{"line":126,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"· 起点：“自我是一种偏见”，是看待世界的独特视角。\n· 发展：当偏见被广泛接受，就从“个人智慧”变成“集体智慧”；集体共识就是“定义集体自我的存在”。\n· 终点：智慧是“过去、现在和未来的自己形成的需要保持一致的共识”。这条线索贯穿全文，为所有感性叙事提供了理性注解。","position":{"start":{"line":124,"column":1},"end":{"line":124,"column":1}},"key":"PLejagnn2x"}],"key":"ceb5LkY8P1"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":128,"column":1},"end":{"line":128,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"这四条线索的关系是：","position":{"start":{"line":128,"column":1},"end":{"line":128,"column":1}},"key":"qjCceHY01p"}],"key":"gWKmlCeISn"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":130,"column":1},"end":{"line":133,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"· 时间线索提供情感动力（为什么做）\n· 身份线索锚定社会角色（我是谁）\n· 创造线索呈现具体实践（做什么）\n· 哲学线索赋予终极意义（为什么这很重要）","position":{"start":{"line":130,"column":1},"end":{"line":130,"column":1}},"key":"SahOLhEjJu"}],"key":"f89zDm96yd"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":135,"column":1},"end":{"line":135,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value